    "A member of the Cambridge Philosophical [i.e., scientific] Society, the group's topics encompassed building construction, including medieval arches.": [],
    "As a scientist and inventor, he investigated topics such as human vowel sounds (1828-1832) and the possibility of talking machines.": [],
